WEBVTT

00:06.499 --> 00:07.840
(Respect copyright)

00:14.112 --> 00:20.704
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

00:24.288 --> 00:30.432
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

00:32.640 --> 00:35.872
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

00:36.096 --> 00:42.112
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

00:42.432 --> 00:45.856
♪To the horizon's call♪

00:45.920 --> 00:52.480
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

00:53.536 --> 00:57.472
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

00:57.472 --> 01:03.552
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

01:03.840 --> 01:07.712
♪Put every twist behind you♪

01:07.712 --> 01:12.576
♪Drift leisurely through time♪

01:12.960 --> 01:15.680
♪Make headway against the wind♪

01:15.680 --> 01:18.667
♪Let mountains bow to your pace♪

01:18.720 --> 01:24.128
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

01:24.640 --> 01:28.579
♪Let your nature burst free♪

01:30.240 --> 01:34.490
=The First Jasmine=

01:34.960 --> 01:37.644
=Episode 11=

01:40.066 --> 01:40.866
Where is she?

01:42.706 --> 01:43.506
'She'?

01:46.506 --> 01:47.306
Who is 'she'?

01:50.146 --> 01:52.226
Taking payment and clearing trouble.

01:52.625 --> 01:53.625
Repeat that.

01:55.345 --> 01:57.985
Taking payment and clearing trouble.

02:01.745 --> 02:02.586
You, sir!

02:02.985 --> 02:04.506
It's you, sir.

02:04.745 --> 02:06.666
I wonder why you looked so familiar.

02:07.185 --> 02:08.465
You spent money quite fast.

02:08.465 --> 02:10.106
Well, you...

02:11.225 --> 02:14.465
We know the time, the place,

02:15.546 --> 02:17.185
and the things you bought.

02:18.146 --> 02:19.505
I offer a chance to you.

02:19.986 --> 02:22.665
Talk here,
or back at Jingzhao Prefecture.

02:23.625 --> 02:26.785
Then... I'll definitely talk here.

02:40.386 --> 02:43.706
I know. You're looking for that woman.

02:43.745 --> 02:46.306
Yes. I-I remember that woman,

02:46.625 --> 02:48.146
but I truly don't know where she is.

02:48.146 --> 02:49.986
We were just about to catch her,

02:49.986 --> 02:52.986
but a swordsman
suddenly appeared and rescued her.

02:54.345 --> 02:55.266
Why were you after her?

02:56.505 --> 03:00.065
A while back,
the Red Scorpion Gang took a big job.

03:00.225 --> 03:03.586
The client paid us a huge sum
to catch this woman.

03:03.945 --> 03:05.665
Do you know that woman's identity?

03:06.185 --> 03:08.785
I don't know. Wait, I truly don't know.

03:08.785 --> 03:11.185
We were only given this location

03:11.185 --> 03:13.266
and told when to act.

03:13.625 --> 03:16.706
Any distinctive features
about the swordsman who rescued her?

03:17.426 --> 03:19.426
T-That swordsman...

03:22.945 --> 03:23.445
Go.

03:25.826 --> 03:27.306
He looked like an average man.

03:27.306 --> 03:29.386
Well, he's not too tall or too short.

03:30.026 --> 03:32.272
But his swordsmanship is superb,
striking like lightning.

03:32.586 --> 03:34.945
We didn't see other details clearly.

03:35.866 --> 03:37.945
Then you kept pursuing her

03:40.386 --> 03:41.986
and forced her off the cliff?

03:42.225 --> 03:43.225
No.

03:43.866 --> 03:45.665
That swordsman's skills are incredible.

03:45.665 --> 03:47.146
We fought and knew we couldn't win,

03:47.146 --> 03:48.345
so we retreated.

03:52.225 --> 03:53.625
One last question.

03:55.225 --> 03:56.345
Who's the client?

04:51.626 --> 04:53.545
I smell a strong jasmine fragrance.

04:54.066 --> 04:55.266
Did you burn incense?

04:57.665 --> 04:59.186
The gardener delivered flowers.

04:59.225 --> 05:01.946
The villa lord makes scent beads
from seasonal flowers every quarter.

05:03.985 --> 05:05.665
How old is your villa lord?

05:06.985 --> 05:07.865
I don't know.

05:07.946 --> 05:10.266
He looks around twenty.

05:11.105 --> 05:12.345
That young?

05:14.105 --> 05:15.506
Not what I expected.

05:15.706 --> 05:17.066
I thought he'd be an elder.

05:17.266 --> 05:19.266
Our villa lord just got married.

05:19.266 --> 05:20.425
He's a young talent,

05:20.425 --> 05:21.586
well-versed in the six arts,

05:21.586 --> 05:23.225
quite famous in the capital...

05:27.506 --> 05:29.946
If there's nothing else,
I'll take my leave.

05:41.545 --> 05:43.425
Mr. Wang, mind the moss underfoot.

05:43.785 --> 05:45.665
Alright, got it.

05:59.785 --> 06:01.386
The jasmine smells so refreshing.

06:02.586 --> 06:03.746
Thanks for your appreciation.

06:05.506 --> 06:09.506
I specially selected
these double-petal, two-toned jasmines

06:09.826 --> 06:11.186
for our lord to make scent beads.

06:11.266 --> 06:12.946
They're pleasing to the eye.

06:13.706 --> 06:14.785
Truly exquisite.

06:16.105 --> 06:17.586
Have you served the villa long?

06:18.465 --> 06:20.386
No, I'm a gardener
from the east outskirts.

06:21.026 --> 06:25.225
Every other month, I deliver
twenty pots of seasonal plants here

06:25.225 --> 06:26.506
to earn a meager living.

06:27.706 --> 06:29.946
Would you like to earn extra money?

06:31.826 --> 06:33.066
Do you need flowers too?

06:34.785 --> 06:36.066
Please come closer.

06:42.026 --> 06:42.946
Please speak.

06:44.146 --> 06:46.305
Help me deliver a message
to the capital.

06:46.706 --> 06:48.146
I offer you a hundred guan for this.

06:48.826 --> 06:52.105
What message, and to whom?

07:03.186 --> 07:05.266
Why isn't there any news for so long?

07:12.465 --> 07:13.266
Your Highness.

07:14.105 --> 07:15.506
Why do you look so panicked?

07:16.865 --> 07:20.626
I saw many guards from Jingzhao Prefecture
heading out of the city.

07:20.946 --> 07:23.105
Seems something major has happened.

07:24.545 --> 07:26.105
How did it get so out of hand?

07:27.425 --> 07:28.266
Your Highness.

07:31.345 --> 07:32.186
Where's His Highness?

07:32.225 --> 07:35.105
It seems His Highness went
to Songyue Mountain Villa.

07:38.066 --> 07:38.865
Get the carriage.

07:39.506 --> 07:40.146
Yes.

07:42.800 --> 07:43.419
Hyah.

07:46.465 --> 07:48.105
Songyue Mountain Villa.

07:53.545 --> 07:54.785
Is it this way?

07:55.506 --> 07:56.545
Probably.

07:56.905 --> 07:57.946
How do you know?

07:59.146 --> 08:00.985
Didn't you ask me to inquire?

08:01.746 --> 08:05.146
You said aside from
practicing the guqin at home,

08:05.425 --> 08:06.985
His Highness goes to the palace.

08:07.826 --> 08:09.785
You wondered where else he might go.

08:09.905 --> 08:11.146
Did I say that?

08:16.266 --> 08:18.425
Your Highness, are you alright?

08:19.146 --> 08:20.545
Do you even know how to drive?

08:20.905 --> 08:21.785
What happened?

08:27.985 --> 08:28.785
Your Highness,

08:29.545 --> 08:30.746
someone's lying in the way,

08:30.746 --> 08:31.785
covered in blood.

08:32.665 --> 08:33.626
Go around him.

08:56.945 --> 08:57.746
Wait!

09:06.466 --> 09:08.905
Your Highness,
there's news of Her Highness.

09:17.185 --> 09:19.026
Your Highness, do you know him?

09:20.266 --> 09:21.106
No.

09:22.585 --> 09:24.825
Then why save him?

09:26.266 --> 09:27.905
I can't just watch him die.

09:30.585 --> 09:31.386
Well...

09:33.146 --> 09:33.986
Go away.

09:34.626 --> 09:35.425
Yes.

09:39.825 --> 09:41.264
His tri-jiao meridian is reversed.

09:41.705 --> 09:42.866
His Qihai point is blocked.

09:43.266 --> 09:45.425
How did he get so severely injured?

09:46.146 --> 09:47.386
Did you mistreat him?

09:48.626 --> 09:49.585
How would I know?

09:49.945 --> 09:51.305
Just treat him.

09:57.466 --> 09:59.545
Why take off his clothes?

10:00.346 --> 10:02.425
How can I treat him
without taking off his clothes?

10:39.065 --> 10:40.226
Are you alright?

10:43.705 --> 10:45.626
Tell Mo Jingli to come see me.

11:06.026 --> 11:07.346
Your eyes are fine now?

11:07.866 --> 11:10.626
Is there anywhere else
you're uncomfortable?

11:19.226 --> 11:20.506
You had many injuries.

11:22.146 --> 11:22.986
Does it hurt?

11:24.866 --> 11:26.986
I'll have the physician
examine you again.

11:38.705 --> 11:40.506
I didn't mean to hide it from you.

11:41.226 --> 11:44.986
I was afraid if you knew it was me,
you wouldn't rest and recover.

11:46.785 --> 11:48.146
I only wanted you to get better.

11:53.746 --> 11:57.986
Li, please don't look at me
like that, alright?

12:00.705 --> 12:01.545
I want to leave.

12:01.705 --> 12:02.825
But you haven't recovered.

12:02.825 --> 12:03.785
I said,

12:04.785 --> 12:05.545
I want to leave.

12:06.266 --> 12:08.626
Li, I was wrong.

12:08.785 --> 12:09.705
Please don't be angry.

12:10.106 --> 12:12.146
You refused to speak to me
and I had no choice.

12:12.825 --> 12:15.705
I heard you went to Zhengyi Temple.

12:16.665 --> 12:17.746
I wanted to see you,

12:17.986 --> 12:21.106
but when I arrived,
you'd already entered the temple.

12:22.065 --> 12:23.506
So I waited outside.

12:23.705 --> 12:25.626
I waited several days
before you came out.

12:26.945 --> 12:27.746
But...

12:29.266 --> 12:30.746
But you were with him.

12:32.466 --> 12:33.785
I meant to leave,

12:34.665 --> 12:35.945
but you were attacked.

12:36.665 --> 12:38.705
When I got there,
you had fallen off the cliff.

12:40.346 --> 12:41.026
Li.

12:43.106 --> 12:43.986
Do you know

12:45.785 --> 12:49.346
how I felt seeing you in danger?

12:52.866 --> 12:54.226
How did you feel?

12:55.905 --> 12:58.346
While you're here with me,

12:58.672 --> 13:00.346
have you thought about
how Ye Ying feels?

13:00.425 --> 13:01.705
I didn't want to marry her.

13:01.825 --> 13:02.746
Mo Jingli!

13:09.106 --> 13:10.146
I'll say it again.

13:11.266 --> 13:12.226
Stay away from me.

13:15.106 --> 13:17.026
Li, don't go.

13:17.746 --> 13:19.785
Li, your wounds haven't fully healed.

13:19.785 --> 13:20.506
(Songyue Mountain Villa)
Li.

13:22.785 --> 13:24.266
Y-Your wounds...

13:25.866 --> 13:26.585
Li.

13:40.866 --> 13:42.825
Li, your wounds...

13:51.665 --> 13:52.466
Mo Jingli.

13:53.905 --> 13:54.866
I've made myself clear.

13:55.866 --> 13:57.146
I have nothing to do with you.

13:57.266 --> 13:58.905
Please don't show up before me again.

13:58.905 --> 13:59.785
Don't you understand?

13:59.785 --> 14:01.146
What would you do without me?

14:02.466 --> 14:04.506
When you were off the cliff,
poisoned, and injured,

14:04.506 --> 14:05.585
I saved you.

14:05.585 --> 14:06.785
I didn't need you to save me.

14:11.226 --> 14:12.026
Why?

14:14.305 --> 14:15.705
You don't know why?

14:18.185 --> 14:18.986
Mo Jingli.

14:20.425 --> 14:23.346
Before I came down the mountain,
I told myself

14:23.545 --> 14:24.986
to pretend I'd never met you.

14:26.585 --> 14:28.425
Please don't push me further.

14:32.866 --> 14:33.825
I understand now.

14:34.266 --> 14:37.626
You blame me for those deaths.

14:38.585 --> 14:41.425
You want to kill me and avenge them,

14:43.466 --> 14:44.266
right?

14:51.425 --> 14:53.466
Go ahead. Kill me.

14:53.705 --> 14:55.346
Go on. Kill me.

15:02.785 --> 15:03.545
Are you insane?

15:34.185 --> 15:34.986
Li.

15:36.585 --> 15:37.746
Li, you didn't leave.

15:42.026 --> 15:42.825
Li.

15:44.266 --> 15:47.026
You still care about me, don't you?

15:51.266 --> 15:54.386
Don't worry. I won't die that easily.

16:02.665 --> 16:06.026
When I was little, I loved sweets,

16:06.785 --> 16:07.905
so I always had toothaches.

16:10.026 --> 16:12.945
Senior Guan once taught me
a method to relieve pain.

16:13.506 --> 16:16.346
He said to press hard on the Hegu point

16:16.866 --> 16:18.626
on the outer side of the thenar space.

16:19.585 --> 16:23.506
Pressing dozens of times each session
could release blockages and ease pain.

16:26.026 --> 16:27.346
Whether it's a toothache,

16:27.905 --> 16:32.585
or bumps, bruises, and injuries
on the body, this method works well.

16:36.146 --> 16:38.146
I heard he died
under a volley of arrows.

16:39.106 --> 16:40.545
Did it hurt when he died?

16:42.665 --> 16:45.626
Did he have time
to press the Hegu point?

16:47.705 --> 16:49.866
Senior Chen loved children the most.

16:50.466 --> 16:52.185
When he learned his wife was pregnant,

16:52.986 --> 16:54.785
he was so happy
he couldn't sleep all night.

16:56.665 --> 16:57.466
This year,

16:58.785 --> 17:00.545
his child reaches eight,

17:00.986 --> 17:03.545
yet still doesn't know
what his father looked like.

17:04.986 --> 17:06.585
Junior Zhou was the youngest.

17:07.466 --> 17:09.466
He was only twelve years old back then.

17:12.026 --> 17:17.785
He volunteered for the escort
because he liked you.

17:19.065 --> 17:22.825
Mo Jingli, they all died because of you.

17:25.385 --> 17:27.266
I am one of Lishan Academy.

17:29.145 --> 17:31.065
I can never forgive you.

17:33.145 --> 17:35.266
Li, listen to me.

17:35.305 --> 17:36.466
Don't tell me any excuses.

17:36.466 --> 17:37.706
I won't hear any of it.

17:43.785 --> 17:46.746
You should be glad
you broke off the engagement.

17:48.785 --> 17:52.105
Otherwise, I might lose control
and kill you on our wedding day.

18:04.825 --> 18:08.506
Tell those people outside to leave.
I'm leaving this place.

18:09.385 --> 18:10.266
No one move!

18:10.825 --> 18:12.426
We are the Jingzhao Prefecture!

18:12.426 --> 18:13.986
Everyone, stay where you are!

18:13.986 --> 18:16.305
- Li.
- Any resistance will be arrested.

18:18.926 --> 18:21.706
- Your Highness.
- Li!

18:21.706 --> 18:22.320
Your Highness.

18:25.545 --> 18:26.506
You're injured.

18:28.706 --> 18:29.305
It's nothing.

18:42.345 --> 18:42.986
Let's go.

19:02.736 --> 19:05.328
(Cloth)

19:11.706 --> 19:12.545
You woke up?

19:17.625 --> 19:18.426
It's you?

19:20.545 --> 19:22.825
Stop playing dead. Get up.

19:29.385 --> 19:30.785
Who else could it be?

19:31.746 --> 19:33.666
You even claimed to be
a martial art master?

19:33.946 --> 19:36.746
If not for me, you would
have died by the roadside.

19:36.946 --> 19:39.145
You're a noble lady
from an official family,

19:39.266 --> 19:40.746
and you married a current prince.

19:41.305 --> 19:42.746
Why do you speak so viciously?

19:43.226 --> 19:44.266
How do you know?

19:44.865 --> 19:46.345
Since I took your job,

19:46.986 --> 19:48.666
how could I not know who my employer is?

19:50.226 --> 19:51.345
You investigated me?

19:52.865 --> 19:55.545
Let me ask you, did she die or not?

19:55.666 --> 19:56.906
You want her dead that badly?

19:58.545 --> 19:59.746
I don't care.

20:00.305 --> 20:01.906
I just want to know the outcome.

20:03.305 --> 20:05.785
Tell me, what exactly happened to her?

20:05.785 --> 20:06.906
She fell off a cliff.

20:07.706 --> 20:08.946
But I didn't push her.

20:08.986 --> 20:10.466
She fell down herself.

20:15.746 --> 20:16.545
Is she dead?

20:17.065 --> 20:18.305
But she was rescued.

20:22.065 --> 20:23.986
Can't you just say it all at once?

20:27.545 --> 20:29.065
Since you wanted me to hurt her,

20:29.825 --> 20:31.746
why do you look like
you don't want her dead?

20:31.986 --> 20:32.865
Not your business.

20:36.266 --> 20:38.545
This matter is settled.
It has nothing to do with you.

20:39.186 --> 20:40.305
Farewell.

20:43.568 --> 20:49.552
(Prince Ding's Mansion)

20:53.145 --> 20:54.706
They're back. Hurry!

21:26.946 --> 21:27.545
Li...

21:28.266 --> 21:29.345
She's still asleep.

21:29.825 --> 21:30.625
Go back for now.

21:31.065 --> 21:32.105
Alright.

21:44.944 --> 21:49.328
(Tuisi Pavilion)

23:02.226 --> 23:04.105
(Another group of assassins
in the forest.)

23:09.145 --> 23:10.865
My lady, see if you like this.

23:12.105 --> 23:12.906
Come.

23:12.906 --> 23:14.345
- Alright.
- Show me that one.

23:14.345 --> 23:15.145
Okay.

23:19.825 --> 23:20.785
Paid for both tables?

23:21.145 --> 23:21.666
Yes.

23:21.706 --> 23:23.946
Sir, a meal or a room?

23:23.946 --> 23:24.625
Find someone.

23:25.065 --> 23:27.226
Find someone? Who?

23:27.545 --> 23:29.065
An injured young man.

23:29.145 --> 23:31.706
The physician at Renyi Hall said
he's staying here.

23:32.385 --> 23:34.105
I'm his friend, here to visit him.

23:39.706 --> 23:41.065
I do recall now.

23:41.065 --> 23:41.946
Take me to him.

23:41.946 --> 23:42.706
This way, please.

23:45.545 --> 23:47.385
This way, sir. Mind the steps.

23:49.145 --> 23:51.065
Perfect. This man is looking for you.

24:29.145 --> 24:30.305
Who exactly are you?

24:31.625 --> 24:32.426
Your friend.

24:34.585 --> 24:37.466
Your Highness, are you in?

24:44.385 --> 24:45.466
Where has she gone?

24:46.385 --> 24:47.946
Her Highness may have gone out.

24:48.946 --> 24:51.345
Your Highness,
you didn't rest well last night.

24:51.345 --> 24:52.706
Perhaps you should take some rest.

24:52.906 --> 24:53.706
Go find her.

24:55.545 --> 24:56.305
Yes.

24:57.266 --> 24:58.065
Tao.

24:59.186 --> 24:59.986
Your Highness.

25:00.385 --> 25:01.305
Where is she?

25:01.825 --> 25:05.785
Her Highness went out
to Shende Shop early this morning.

25:05.865 --> 25:07.345
Qingyu went with her.

25:11.226 --> 25:12.026
Go find her.

25:12.706 --> 25:13.506
Yes.

25:15.946 --> 25:17.426
Come and take a look.

25:18.865 --> 25:20.426
Come take a look.

25:20.426 --> 25:21.585
The quality is quite good.

25:22.345 --> 25:23.585
Come take a look.

25:24.385 --> 25:26.865
W-What is so urgent?

25:26.865 --> 25:28.785
Must you go personally?

25:29.305 --> 25:30.585
After suffering so much,

25:30.585 --> 25:33.305
before even fully recovering,
yet you're out now.

25:34.706 --> 25:37.266
Candied hawthorn!

25:37.545 --> 25:39.266
Candied hawthorn!

25:39.266 --> 25:40.426
Give me two skewers.

25:40.986 --> 25:41.666
Right away.

26:17.785 --> 26:20.105
Captain Li Zhao?

26:21.466 --> 26:23.506
How are you? Are you badly hurt?

26:24.946 --> 26:26.706
It's nothing, just a flesh wound.

26:27.666 --> 26:28.506
Where is he?

26:28.906 --> 26:29.706
Inside.

26:31.186 --> 26:32.105
You wait here.

26:32.746 --> 26:33.506
Yes.

26:40.545 --> 26:41.345
It's him, isn't it?

26:42.466 --> 26:43.466
Did you interrogate him?

26:43.946 --> 26:46.946
No. We simply fought a few moves.

26:46.946 --> 26:48.305
He was already injured.

26:48.345 --> 26:50.145
Don't worry. He won't die.

26:50.986 --> 26:51.946
Wake him up.

26:56.506 --> 26:58.145
Friend, wake up.

27:08.946 --> 27:10.466
Who sent you to kill me?

27:13.585 --> 27:14.385
It's you.

27:15.226 --> 27:16.345
You escaped too?

27:17.426 --> 27:19.385
Thanks to you, I'm still alive.

27:20.026 --> 27:22.865
Was it you who saved me
on the ox cart earlier?

27:25.585 --> 27:26.385
Yes.

27:29.266 --> 27:30.746
I didn't know it was you at the time.

27:32.145 --> 27:33.385
But why didn't you tell me?

27:34.065 --> 27:37.345
Stories like repaying kindness
are too cliché. I hate them.

27:39.266 --> 27:42.706
Besides, isn't it normal for someone
like you to bite the hand that feeds?

27:43.305 --> 27:44.785
I didn't mean to harm you.

27:44.865 --> 27:46.345
I didn't know you were Princess Ding.

27:47.026 --> 27:48.785
Then tell me the person behind you.

27:54.426 --> 27:55.226
Refuse to talk?

28:10.305 --> 28:11.145
My next cut

28:12.426 --> 28:13.785
will land right here.

28:14.145 --> 28:16.065
I harmed you. I'm sorry.

28:16.426 --> 28:18.545
You saved me, yet I harmed you.

28:18.946 --> 28:21.946
I owe you a life.
It's only right if you take it back.

28:24.545 --> 28:26.545
It's that foolish woman!
That foolish woman!

28:26.785 --> 28:27.585
It's...

28:32.506 --> 28:33.986
She actually didn't want to kill you.

28:35.065 --> 28:36.145
But I messed it up.

28:49.466 --> 28:50.746
What do we do with this kid?

28:51.426 --> 28:52.226
As you wish.

28:52.305 --> 28:53.145
As I wish?

28:54.145 --> 28:55.186
He won't tell others.

28:57.145 --> 28:59.946
What do we do next? That woman
is scheming against you.

28:59.946 --> 29:01.865
If we don't deal with her,
it might happen again.

29:03.666 --> 29:05.226
I have a rough idea who it is.

29:13.385 --> 29:15.305
This is Princess Li.
How dare you stop her?

29:22.986 --> 29:24.145
You may withdraw.

29:30.226 --> 29:32.145
May I ask why you seek His Highness?

29:32.145 --> 29:34.385
This is Prince Li's Mansion.
And I am Princess Li.

29:34.785 --> 29:37.266
Do I need a reason to see His Highness?

29:37.426 --> 29:38.706
You are absolutely right.

29:38.706 --> 29:40.746
But His Highness
is discussing important matters.

29:40.746 --> 29:43.746
It may not be appropriate
for you to barge in unannounced.

29:44.105 --> 29:46.512
Does discussing important matters
require music and dancers?

29:47.466 --> 29:48.785
Is he discussing matters

29:48.825 --> 29:50.585
or just trying to avoid me?

29:53.186 --> 29:53.986
Move!

29:59.824 --> 30:00.625
(Tingyue Pavilion)

30:00.625 --> 30:03.065
This is wine from the Western Regions.

30:03.545 --> 30:05.186
One jar could buy a house.

30:05.746 --> 30:07.785
Then we must drink more.

30:07.785 --> 30:10.506
Drink the treasures into our bellies.

30:10.506 --> 30:11.506
Exactly.

30:11.545 --> 30:12.305
Cheers.

30:12.625 --> 30:16.666
Your Highness,
is this your princess consort?

30:16.986 --> 30:18.266
She's quite feisty.

30:18.266 --> 30:20.506
I've long heard Princess Li
is exceptionally beautiful.

30:20.666 --> 30:23.065
You truly live up to your reputation.

30:23.145 --> 30:25.666
Why not drink with us?

30:28.065 --> 30:29.545
Why such a temper?

30:31.625 --> 30:34.145
Your Highness,
do you despise me this much?

30:37.506 --> 30:40.345
Although my father sought this marriage,

30:40.946 --> 30:42.768
you had broken off
the previous engagement.

30:43.145 --> 30:45.266
If you were unwilling,
you could have simply refused.

30:45.545 --> 30:48.666
Since you married me,
I am your rightful princess consort.

30:48.746 --> 30:50.466
Why do you humiliate me like this?

30:58.266 --> 30:59.585
Are you even listening to me?

31:02.585 --> 31:05.746
Why are you so angry? Calm down.

31:05.746 --> 31:07.385
Come on, cheers.

31:08.305 --> 31:09.105
Get out!

31:10.105 --> 31:10.906
Get out!

31:12.105 --> 31:12.706
Get out!

31:12.946 --> 31:13.706
Go, go.

31:13.706 --> 31:14.305
Go.

31:15.746 --> 31:16.506
Get out!

31:17.065 --> 31:17.825
Let's go now.

31:40.145 --> 31:42.585
So, it was Mo Jingli who saved you?

31:42.906 --> 31:43.906
It was Master Zhu.

31:44.706 --> 31:45.706
Master Zhu?

31:47.385 --> 31:49.706
When I fell off the cliff,
with my life in danger,

31:50.506 --> 31:52.906
I thought I'd be dead for sure.

32:05.200 --> 32:06.832
(Master Zhu, Lishan Academy)

32:28.666 --> 32:31.545
Luckily, Master Zhu
appeared in time and saved me.

32:31.545 --> 32:32.775
He used a branch as a sword

32:32.775 --> 32:34.785
to kill the snakes
at the bottom of the cliff.

32:35.065 --> 32:37.466
But there were too many snakes,
and I was bitten.

32:37.585 --> 32:38.986
Then I passed out.

32:40.585 --> 32:43.865
Lishan Mountain has long been sealed off.
How could Master Zhu come down?

32:44.226 --> 32:46.865
Besides, Master Zhu is a swordsman.
He never parts with his sword.

32:46.946 --> 32:48.385
Why did he use a branch as a sword?

32:50.305 --> 32:51.305
I don't know.

32:52.720 --> 32:54.506
Lishan Mountain
is in a delicate position.

32:54.506 --> 32:57.625
If anyone discovers Master Zhu
came down, it would bring disaster.

32:59.946 --> 33:02.186
I will search the inns and taverns
along the way.

33:02.506 --> 33:03.906
You pay more attention recently.

33:04.026 --> 33:05.825
Also, take more rest to recover.

33:09.946 --> 33:11.345
Grandmother's birthday is coming.

33:11.345 --> 33:14.192
There's one more thing
I need you to help me with.

33:14.192 --> 33:17.520
(Ye Mansion)

33:42.145 --> 33:44.506
On such a hot day,
why brought me such boiling tea?

33:44.506 --> 33:45.825
What's wrong with you?

33:45.825 --> 33:47.145
My lady, I'll go change it.

33:54.385 --> 33:56.226
My lady, someone delivered a letter.

34:00.208 --> 34:02.736
(Pang)

34:06.946 --> 34:08.225
Why don't you just die?

34:08.225 --> 34:09.225
People die every day.

34:09.225 --> 34:10.625
Some die from starvation, illness,

34:10.625 --> 34:12.506
beaten to death,
or torn apart by horses.

34:12.506 --> 34:14.225
Why are you still alive?

34:18.906 --> 34:23.105
The days are so fine.
How could I bear to leave you behind?

34:23.866 --> 34:27.386
Yuan, you aren't true to yourself.

34:27.826 --> 34:31.745
Do you really want me to die?

34:35.625 --> 34:39.506
Yuan, you have quite a temper.

34:41.946 --> 34:42.946
This is the last time.

34:44.986 --> 34:47.346
You said that last time too.

34:50.745 --> 34:55.506
Yuan, Ying married Prince Li
and became the princess consort.

34:56.906 --> 34:58.346
How has she been lately?

34:59.906 --> 35:01.026
Don't you ever mention her.

35:01.906 --> 35:03.026
I'm warning you.

35:03.625 --> 35:06.946
If you dare go near her, I'll kill you.

35:11.866 --> 35:13.346
Fine, I won't mention her.

35:18.506 --> 35:22.426
Yuan, I didn't mean to go
to the Ye Mansion to find you.

35:22.986 --> 35:25.306
But Shende Shop changed stewards,

35:25.466 --> 35:28.105
and those shops also changed staff.

35:28.185 --> 35:32.745
I truly had no other choice,
so I resorted to this.

35:33.506 --> 35:34.786
You went to Shende Shop?

35:36.185 --> 35:36.745
Yes.

35:36.745 --> 35:37.506
Did you...

35:38.145 --> 35:41.745
Don't worry.
The steward and the staff are all new.

35:41.866 --> 35:44.185
I could tell at a glance
that something's off.

35:44.665 --> 35:46.426
Why would I still barge right in?

35:47.745 --> 35:51.745
Yuan, you are my fortune-bringer,

35:52.145 --> 35:54.346
my guardian deity.

35:54.866 --> 35:57.105
How could I not consider you?

35:57.665 --> 35:59.506
At least you have some sense.

35:59.506 --> 36:02.105
I am a true scholar through and through.

36:02.786 --> 36:06.585
Back then, if it weren't for you
heartlessly abandoning me,

36:07.386 --> 36:11.026
leaving me heartbroken
and losing my composure,

36:11.026 --> 36:14.145
I'd have passed the imperial exams
and become a minister.

36:15.225 --> 36:16.946
How could I end up like this today?

36:20.026 --> 36:20.786
Who is it?

36:25.665 --> 36:26.906
W-What what do you want?

36:28.185 --> 36:28.705
Captain Li.

36:28.705 --> 36:30.866
I just need Mrs. Ye
to do me a small favor.

36:36.466 --> 36:37.986
So where did we go today?

36:39.065 --> 36:41.306
J-Just Captain Li's house.

36:43.386 --> 36:46.225
I went to Shende Shop with you?

36:46.386 --> 36:48.185
What did we do there today?

36:48.545 --> 36:51.105
We went to check on the shop
and look over the accounts.

36:51.986 --> 36:52.665
Your Highness.

36:54.185 --> 36:55.665
Your Highness, you're finally back.

36:55.665 --> 36:56.466
What's the matter?

36:57.506 --> 36:59.426
His Highness hasn't seen you all day.

36:59.426 --> 37:00.665
He has been so worried.

37:00.665 --> 37:02.065
He sent many men to look for you.

37:03.466 --> 37:04.665
Please return now.

37:05.026 --> 37:06.946
Your Highness,
we haven't found Her Highness.

37:06.946 --> 37:07.665
Keep searching.

37:07.745 --> 37:08.346
Yes.

37:12.545 --> 37:13.665
Don't be too anxious.

37:13.705 --> 37:16.185
Li might be on her way back right now.

37:20.585 --> 37:22.585
Your Highness, Her Highness is here.

37:30.065 --> 37:32.306
Why are you back so late?
Where did you go?

37:32.986 --> 37:34.265
Sorry for worrying you.

37:34.466 --> 37:36.306
I'm fine, just walking around.

37:36.466 --> 37:38.866
You still have injuries.
How could you go out?

38:04.866 --> 38:06.306
What do we do, Your Highness?

38:07.906 --> 38:08.946
Keep your mouth shut.

38:13.225 --> 38:14.026
Close the door.

38:26.545 --> 38:28.866
Tell me the truth.
Where did you two go today?

38:30.145 --> 38:32.906
We went to Shende Shop
to look over the accounts.

38:32.906 --> 38:35.946
Nonsense. I went to Shende Shop
twice today to look for you.

38:35.946 --> 38:37.506
There are still people waiting there.

38:37.506 --> 38:38.986
None of you were seen there.

38:46.306 --> 38:49.265
His Highness has really
lost his temper this time.

38:49.506 --> 38:50.745
Her Highness is in big trouble.

38:51.065 --> 38:53.705
Will His Highness
hit or scold Her Highness?

38:54.866 --> 38:59.665
From what I know of His Highness,
he won't hit or scold her.

38:59.946 --> 39:02.786
But he probably won't speak
to Her Highness for the next few days.

39:03.506 --> 39:06.306
And he might give her
the cold shoulder for a while.

39:31.946 --> 39:32.745
Your Highness.

39:34.826 --> 39:36.625
Don't you have anything to say to me?

39:38.545 --> 39:39.346
I...

39:44.906 --> 39:46.145
Where do you think you are?

39:46.625 --> 39:48.986
Lishan Mountain? A Daoist temple?

39:49.665 --> 39:50.705
Free to come and go?

39:51.986 --> 39:52.786
Ye Li.

39:53.705 --> 39:56.145
You wanted to show your face
in public and run shops.

39:56.386 --> 39:57.866
I never interfered.

39:57.968 --> 39:59.786
You wanted to go back
to the mountain, fine.

39:59.786 --> 40:01.866
You were gone for days without any word.

40:02.225 --> 40:03.585
I still didn't interfere.

40:05.026 --> 40:06.306
But trouble came to you.

40:10.026 --> 40:12.145
Yesterday you were finally rescued,

40:12.466 --> 40:14.466
and we still don't know who's after you.

40:15.065 --> 40:17.986
It is also unknown whether
there will be any further danger.

40:19.145 --> 40:22.306
You're gone for a full day today,
sending back no word.

40:23.145 --> 40:24.986
Do you think you are some roaming hero?

40:26.185 --> 40:27.705
Please let me explain.

40:30.065 --> 40:31.105
Don't go.

40:44.426 --> 40:45.346
You're out of line.

40:47.105 --> 40:47.946
Jin, come here.

40:48.545 --> 40:49.346
Don't move.

40:56.866 --> 40:59.506
Weren't you the one
who came angrily to question me?

41:00.306 --> 41:01.745
Why refuse to listen to me?

41:02.506 --> 41:04.386
I want to talk now. Are you listening?

41:11.506 --> 41:14.866
No response? I'll take that as a yes.

41:23.306 --> 41:24.145
I'll do it myself.

41:25.306 --> 41:26.906
Your hand's injured. Don't push it.

41:40.306 --> 41:42.585
I told you, His Highness
can't keep the cold shoulder.

41:42.665 --> 41:44.306
Her Highness won't let him.

41:44.306 --> 41:45.185
What do you think?

42:01.625 --> 42:03.906
What do you want to explain?
I'm listening.

42:09.065 --> 42:11.346
Do you want to know about
my relationship with Prince Li?

42:12.866 --> 42:13.866
No.

42:15.386 --> 42:17.906
You have to. I want to tell you.

42:20.026 --> 42:22.224
Mo Jingli and I have known
each other since childhood.

42:22.386 --> 42:24.208
He was sent to Lishan Mountain
to recuperate.

42:24.306 --> 42:25.545
We grew up together.

42:26.225 --> 42:28.745
Later, the late emperor
decreed our engagement.

42:29.906 --> 42:32.906
(In the Fourteenth Year of Jinghe,
the late emperor fell gravely ill.)

42:33.466 --> 42:35.600
(The late Crown Prince summoned
Mo Jingli urgently.)

42:36.265 --> 42:38.105
(My grandfather
was worried about his safety,)

42:38.506 --> 42:42.065
(so he sent eighteen disciples
of Master Zhu to escort him back.)

42:42.608 --> 42:44.934
(Preview)

42:45.265 --> 42:48.986
Your leg condition has been neglected
too long. It needs breaking and resetting.

42:50.585 --> 42:51.946
It will hurt terribly.

42:52.545 --> 42:53.466
I'm not afraid.

42:53.906 --> 42:54.986
So confident in me?

42:55.906 --> 42:58.866
Since I'm letting you treat me,
naturally I trust you.

42:59.426 --> 43:02.866
There's no harm in trying.
It can't be any worse than now.

43:04.145 --> 43:05.665
I will definitely heal you.

43:15.736 --> 43:22.328
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

43:25.912 --> 43:32.056
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

43:34.264 --> 43:37.496
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

43:37.720 --> 43:43.736
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

43:44.056 --> 43:47.480
♪To the horizon's call♪

43:47.544 --> 43:54.104
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

43:55.160 --> 43:59.096
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

43:59.096 --> 44:04.792
♪Both joy and grief
make the trip worthwhile♪

44:05.304 --> 44:13.912
♪Trying to catch up
to your own lost shadow♪

44:14.808 --> 44:20.312
♪Within the wilds, echoes thrive♪

44:20.312 --> 44:25.816
♪Clear mind leads to a clear path♪

44:25.880 --> 44:29.944
♪Be grateful to your losses♪

44:30.232 --> 44:35.456
♪Make your steps weightless♪

44:36.056 --> 44:39.768
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

44:39.800 --> 44:45.464
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

44:46.232 --> 44:54.200
♪Put every twist behind you,
drift leisurely through time♪

44:55.608 --> 45:00.856
♪Make headway against the wind,
let mountains bow to your pace♪

45:01.112 --> 45:07.016
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

45:07.016 --> 45:11.136
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:11.352 --> 45:16.088
♪Unbound by form♪

45:17.304 --> 45:21.576
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:21.816 --> 45:27.256
♪Unbound by form♪
